
ESSELTE BUSINESS {ESB} UNIT BUYS ANTONSON UNIT
    GARDEN CITY, N.Y., March 2 - Esselte Business Systems Inc's
<purchaser>Esselte Meto</purchaser> division said it has <status>acquired</status> the <acquired>Antonson America
Co</acquired>, a subsidiary of {<seller>Antonson Machines AB</seller>}, of Sweden.
    <purchabr>Esselte</purchabr> said the <acqabr>Antonson</acqabr> unit, based in <acqloc>LaPorte, Indiana</acqloc>,
manufactures <acqbus>scales and label printers</acqbus>. The company said the
purchase is part of a plan to increase the range of retail
electronic scales being offered by <purchabr>Esselte</purchabr> in the U.S.
    It said the acquisition will enble <purchabr>Esselte</purchabr> to increase its
distribution base in its effort to grow in the U.S.
